<head>ART</head>
    <list type="altnames">
<item>CRAFT</item>
    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">藝術</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>One of the ARTS or a METHOD of PRODUCING BEAUTIFUL THINGS in order to AMUSE OR TEACH.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. There is no general concept of art or indeed of the artist in ancient China.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>藝術</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
